            </div>
            <div>
                <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2 tracking-tight">Mugi-Solo Political Intelligence Processor</h2>
                <p className="text-slate-400 text-lg max-w-3xl">
                    Ask complex questions about Ugandan politics. <span className="text-purple-400 font-bold">Mugi-Solo</span> will convene a 
                    <span className="text-purple-400 font-bold"> Council of Historical Strategists </span> 
